# Nexus – Investor & Entrepreneur Collaboration Platform

## Advanced Frontend Internship Project

### Project Overview
Nexus is a collaboration platform designed to connect **Investors** and **Entrepreneurs**. This internship project focuses on enhancing the existing React application by implementing advanced frontend features such as scheduling, video calling, document management, payment simulation, and security improvements.

> **Note:** This project is built on an existing codebase. The objective is to extend and improve the provided application rather than develop it from scratch.

---

## Repository & Deployment

- **Base Repository:** Nexus GitHub Repository (Forked)
- **Base Deployment:** https://nexus-iota-five.vercel.app/login

