# Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone <your-repository-url>
```

Navigate to the project:

```bash
cd nexus
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Run the development server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

or

```bash
npm start
```

